    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. Just to be more specific for the module, what kind of guidance should we give regarding hair? For example, if someone has more natural or textured hair—like braids, locs, or an afro—are there certain ways they should manage it to keep that 'understated and elegant' look you mentioned for the boardroom?",
