    "summary": "The user asks for professional grooming advice for boardroom settings, specifically inquiring how individuals with natural or textured hair (braids, locs, afros) can maintain an \"understated and elegant\" look. The assistant responds by suggesting that textured hair should be \"neatly shaped\" and \"contained,\" and eventually implies that \"sleek, controlled\" looks are preferred because they align better with \"established corporate power structures.\"",
